prompts.frontCover: A humorous watercolor painting of a mischievous, cartoon-style corgi caught in the act of "decorating" for a party. The corgi, wearing a tiny, lopsided party hat, stands proudly next to a toilet, with a long, unspooled ribbon of toilet paper draped all over the floor and even on its head. A few colorful confetti pieces are scattered amongst the toilet paper mess. In the center of the scene, written in beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the greeting "happy birthday". The artwork is a flat 2D design, featuring soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds characteristic of a genuine watercolor painting.
